.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7932634061115307, \"rank\": 0.26061412888854235, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his breakthrough campaign two years ago, Wightman suffered multiple injury setbacks that put his place in Paris under threat.Wightman missed out on qualifying in the 1,500m event in Paris, but was selected to run in the 800m after being granted a medical exemption from the trials.Jake Wightman has pulled out of the Olympics|GETTYDespite his injury woes, Wightman was seen as one of Team GB's gold medal hopefuls for the Paris Olympics.But the Scottish athlete has withdrawn from the Olympic Games due to an injury setback, Team GB have announced.They said: \\\"Jake Wightman has been forced to withdraw from Paris 2024 due to a hamstring injury.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999931528691, \"rank\": 6.847188815457305e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999931528691, \"rank\": 6.847188815457305e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re